<i>noun</i>: 아킬레스 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>아킬레스</dt><br>
<dd>a mythical Greek hero of the Iliad; a foremost Greek warrior at the siege of Troy; when he was a baby his mother tried to make him immortal by bathing him in a magical river but the heel by which she held him remained vulnerable--his `Achilles' heel'</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: Achilles</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
